description:
A new way to collaborate

Empowering teams by messenger, meetings, calendar, docs, and emails. It's all in one place.
Docs
- Users with edit permission for a document can now enter suggestion mode to propose revisions to the content. This feature facilitates proofreading and collaboration, allowing collaborators to accept or reject changes.
Settings
- You can now view an updated list of supported shortcuts in the Feishu desktop app and customize them as needed.
